          "content": [
            {
              "type": "heading2",
              "text": "A Journey Through Emotions",
              "spans": []
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "text": "“The Pink Emotions” campaign was launched during Breast Cancer Awareness Month, reimagining awareness as an emotional journey. Instead of relying on symbolic pink visuals alone, the concept translated the stages of a woman’s healing process — discovery, empowerment, healing, and renewal — into a multi-sensory narrative across digital, retail, and live experiences.",
              "spans": []
            }
          ]
